Content:
This week included some key stability fixes, new streaming functionality, and the 
[link: http://www.jonathanturner.org/2019/10/nushell-0_4_0.html] 0.4.0 release
Detegr fixed some issues with parsing filesizes (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/847] #847
)
jonathandturner released 0.4.0 and did some additional tidying (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/844] #844
)
jonathandturner also added new streaming table support (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/812] #812
)
t-hart added a new from-ssv command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/835] #835
)
andrasio fixed a handful of issues with first, last, and count (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/833] #833
)
wycats continued to improve the new coloring support (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/831] #831
)
wycats also added a way to create unstable features behind flags (#810)
thegedge fixed an issue with how external commands got their values (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/829] #829
)
New docs added by sdfnz (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/836] #836
